1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,100
How confident are you that AI's promise will outweigh the perils?

2
00:00:05,220 --> 00:00:11,260
I'm not confident, but that's what we need to get oriented around.

3
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:14,980
That's why I was surprised AI wasn't really an issue in the last election.

4
00:00:15,260 --> 00:00:17,060
It's definitely got to be shaped.

5
00:00:17,280 --> 00:00:19,840
Hearing you say you're not confident is kind of scary.

6
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:26,280
People should think through how is AI going to reshape our lives.

7
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:31,260
It is a profound change agent.

8
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:38,620
And, you know, I don't think it should just be the people who know the technology because there's a lot of choices about how it gets used.

9
00:00:38,720 --> 00:00:40,340
It will change learning.

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:41,860
It will change the job market.

11
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:45,220
And, you know, I think we can shape that in the right way.

12
00:00:45,340 --> 00:00:50,460
But it'll be, you know, just like nuclear energy, nuclear weapons.

13
00:00:50,700 --> 00:00:53,500
It'll challenge us.
